definition: to hold/to embrace/to wrap around/to gather around (sb)/to throng/to swarm/to support/Taiwan pr. [yong3]
to have/there is/there are/to exist/to be

sentences.english: The case was brought by Mercis Media, Bruna's copyright management firm.
sentences.chinese: 本案原告是米菲的版权拥有者Mercis传媒公司。

sentences.english: And the big money is with the brand advertisers.
sentences.chinese: 而且大品牌广告商拥有更多的广告费用。

sentences.english: Heartless laugh, was the best thing that I have.
sentences.chinese: 隃罏没心没肺的笑，是我拥有的最美好的东西。

sentences.english: A noblewoman holding the rank of viscount in her own right.
sentences.chinese: 本人拥有子爵权利的女子爵。

sentences.english: Grocery stores, for example, will have pricing power they haven't experienced in years.
sentences.chinese: 例如百货店，就拥有几年前没有的价格上的优势。

sentences.english: People seem to sense who is powerful.
sentences.chinese: 人们似乎凭感觉就知道谁拥有权力。

sentences.english: The relics left by the aztecs bespeak a high degree of civilization.
sentences.chinese: 阿兹提克族人的遗迹证明其拥有高度文明。

sentences.english: Consequently, you will find that almost every one owns either a watch or a clock.
sentences.chinese: 因此，你会发现几乎每个人都拥有一只表或一个钟。

sentences.english: Edmond, you have a very beautiful lady-love.
sentences.chinese: 爱德蒙你拥有一位如花似玉的爱人。

sentences.english: The plant has Rapier 80, Availability on 30 meters.
sentences.chinese: 本厂拥有剑杆织机80台，月供货30万米。

sentences.english: The company has advanced technology equipment and pipe sound detection equipment.
sentences.chinese: 公司拥有先进的制管工艺设备和完善的检测设备。

sentences.english: Brilliance Auto has two complete vehicle brands of "Brilliance" and "Jinbei".
sentences.chinese: 华晨汽车拥有“中华”和“金杯”两大整车品牌。

sentences.english: Ultimately, being with a true soul partner is all about being purposeful in love.
sentences.chinese: 在爱情中拥有一位真正的灵魂伴侣是每个人所希冀的。

sentences.english: Are there any other policies covering the helper?
sentences.chinese: 家佣是否拥有其他保险？

sentences.english: We are all cool kids with our own interests.
sentences.chinese: 我们都是拥有自己兴趣的酷孩子。

sentences.english: Correlation analysis showed there was relationship between pet owning and health.
sentences.chinese: 相关分析表明，是否拥有宠物犬与身心健康显著相关。
